name.description: The name of the domain. If omitted, this provider will assign a random, unique name.

namePrefix.description: Creates a unique name beginning with the specified prefix. Conflicts with `name`.

tags.description: Key-value map of resource tags. .If configured with a provider `default_tags` configuration block present, tags with matching keys will overwrite those defined at the provider-level.

tagsAll.description: A map of tags assigned to the resource, including those inherited from the provider `default_tags` configuration block.

workflowExecutionRetentionPeriodInDays.description: Length of time that SWF will continue to retain information about the workflow execution after the workflow execution is complete, must be between 0 and 90 days.
